11. Ne5
11. Qb5
12. a3{ Black has managed to find the only safe square for his queen, but even here his position is far from safe, with White able to ratchet up the pressure through  axb4  or simply  Qd4 .     In short, there's full compensation for the double gambit, one we'll return to in the 3... c5  lines.  }
