4. b4
5. Bxc4
5. e6
6. O-O{ Safely housing the king and with a pleasant edge, as well as one where we don't have to go into a QGA structure with  d2 - d4 , but can instead place the pawn on  d3 . }
6. Nf6
7. d3
7. Nbd7
