6. O-O
7. Be2( { Here first, not }7.Qc2 { to avoid the Shankland-endorsed riposte of }7...e5 { . } )( { With the bishop on  e2  and queen still on  d1 , White is much better placed to meet   }7...e5 { with the thematic }8.cxd5 cxd5 9.Nb5 { . } )
