7. Bc4{ With ... axb4  off the agenda for now, it makes sense to bring the light-squared bishop to its best post. White is now very much able to consider ideas of  Qb3  after all, as well as just  O-O  and  Bb2 , increasing the pressure on  d4 .     It may also be possible to go  b4 - b5 , aiming to seize an early initiative by pressuring  c6 , or just  a2 - a3  to secure the queenside. }
