7. Qf6
8. Nc3{ An important move, continuing development, while overprotecting  e4  and supporting  d4 - d5 . }( { White is even now threatening to go   }9.Qa4 Qxf3 10.Rg1 { , }{ leaving Black either in huge trouble down the  a4 - e8  diagonal or after }10...O-O-O 11.Ba6! { . } )
