3. Be7
4. b3( { We don't let Black's unusual early bishop move deter us and continue the standard queenside plan. Now }4...Nf6 5.Bb2 { is, of course, the same as }{   }3...Nf6 4.b3 Be7 5.Bb2 { , but Black can also contest the long diagonal. } )
