9. Bxc4
9. Bb7
10. a4{ This continued to annex space in Daneshvar-Deac, Titled Tuesday Blitz 2022, where White had ideas of both  a4 - a5  and  b4 - b5 , as well as just completing development with  Ba3  and  Qb3 . }
