10. Be2
10. O-O
11. O-O{ White harmoniously completes development, as in Goganov-Agasarov, Yerevan 2022, where  Rc1  might be next up, looking to obtain some pressure on the queenside after  Nxc6   bxc6 ;  Na4 . }
