13. Nd2( { Consistent and stronger than the }13.a5 { of Demuth-Bianchi, Cappelle-la-Grande 2020, as the knight heads for  c4 . } )
13. Bc7
14. f4( { Detonating Black's centre is even stronger than }14.Nc4 { . } )
14. exf4
15. e5{ Black is simply getting smothered by White's powerful centre and with  Ne4  or  Nc4  followed by  Bxf4  on the way. }
