13. Qxg5
14. cxd5( { White was now left dominating the whole board and Black quickly crushed after }14...Qg2 15.Qxe4 { in Herraiz Hidalgo-Serrano Salvador, Madrid 2010, but what happens if he instead holds his centre together? } )
