12. Nxe4( { A new try, not without practical sting and one which might just stun an opponent. We should definitely avoid }12.Rxg4? exf3 { when ...  Ne5  is coming, but }{   }12.Nd4 Nge5 13.cxd5 { is by no means impossible. } )
12. dxe4
13. Qxe4( { The tactics work for White, as after }13...Nge5 14.Nxe5 { there's always  f2 - f4  if needed, while }{   }13...f5? { fails to }14.Qe6+ { . } )
