14. e5
15. c5{ A powerful pawn sacrifice to clear  c4  for the light-squared bishop and smash up Black's pawns. }
15. bxc5
16. dxe5
16. Nxe5
17. Na4{ White will regain the pawn, leaving him with the better structure and more harmonious pieces. }
